# 2p_team_change — host side. Sits in lobby (TDM mode) while the
# client sends a team_change RED → BLUE. Verifies the wire and the
# server-side lobby UI update propagate correctly.
#
# Pairs with 2p_team_change.client.shot which sends the team change
# at tick 100. Host sits idle and re-renders.

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/host_team_change
network host 24025
name HostA

# auto_start_seconds=4 from soldut.cfg → auto-start fires at tick ~240.
# Capture lobby pre-team-change at tick 90 (handshake settled).
at 90  shot t90_pre_team_change

# Capture post-change at tick 200 (still in lobby; auto_start hasn't fired).
at 200 shot t200_post_team_change

# Run past the round start so the inner run.sh assertions pass.
at 600 end
